266
00:12:51,236 --> 00:12:52,370
"How am I doing?"

267
00:12:52,570 --> 00:12:54,873
I was promised a riverboat journey

268
00:12:55,073 --> 00:12:57,142
into the jungles of my subconscious.

269
00:12:57,342 --> 00:12:59,044
