320
00:15:11,242 --> 00:15:13,244
And my mother could've told me before

321
00:15:13,444 --> 00:15:17,284
instead of at the ceremony
in front of everyone.

322
00:15:17,615 --> 00:15:18,550
So, I hear you saying

323
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:21,886
you're angry with your mother.

324
00:15:22,086 --> 00:15:24,989
Damn right, I'm angry with my mother.

325
00:15:25,189 --> 00:15:27,290
