to introduce the winner

339
00:16:03,094 --> 00:16:05,396
of this year's Chancellor's
award for Science

340
00:16:05,596 --> 00:16:08,716
and my good friend,
Dr. Sheldon Cooper.

341
00:16:09,701 --> 00:16:11,536
But before I do,

342
00:16:11,736 --> 00:16:14,138
I'd like to share with you a
letter from Sheldon's mother,

343
00:16:14,338 --> 00:16:16,674
